      • finish

        public static long finish(java.lang.Object context)
        Finds the total number of milliseconds it took and removes the context.
        Parameters:
        context - The context to reference the starting time.
        Returns:
        The time in milliseconds it took between calling start(Object) and this method.
        Returns -1 if we have no record of ever starting.

      • mark

        public static long mark(java.lang.Object context)
        Finds the total number of milliseconds it took. Be sure to still call finish(Object) as this method is only used for checkpoints.
        Parameters:
        context - The context to reference the starting time.
        Returns:
        The time in milliseconds it took between calling start(Object) and this method.
        Returns -1 if we have no record of ever starting.
